OL,3,CTory MPs demand review of Bank of
OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,FA group of Conservative backbenchers
OL,7,Fhave demanded a review of the Bank of
OL,8,FEngland's independence, accusing it of
OL,9,Fcosting taxpayers thousands of pounds
OL,10,Fwith its management.
OL,12,FThe group of 44 MPs said they were
OL,13,F"deeply concerned that the Bank of
OL,14,FEngland is out of step with the
OL,15,Fcentral banks of most major economies"
OL,16,Fin its approach to quantitative
OL,17,Ftightening (QT) ` the selling of
OL,18,Fgovernment bonds the Bank had
OL,19,Fpreviously bought up in an effort to
OL,20,Fstabilise the economy.
