OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,FIn a letter to the chancellor, the MPs
OL,7,Fcriticised the Bank for making
OL,8,Ftaxpayers liable for any losses it
OL,9,Fmade in selling the bonds ` which
OL,10,Fmeant the public faced significant
OL,11,Fcosts "with no public or parliamentary
OL,12,Fdebate or consultation".
OL,14,FThey endorsed a report by pressure
OL,15,Fgroup Conservative Way Forward, which
OL,16,Fsaid making taxpayers liable for
OL,17,Flosses would cost households #4,361
OL,18,Feach between 2023 and 2025.
OL,26,@sD@GOUtD@WO]
