OL,3,CTory MPs demand review of Bank of
OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,FThe report also blamed the Bank for
OL,7,Fthe UK experiencing higher inflation
OL,8,Fthan comparable countries, saying this
OL,9,Fhad cost families #1,185 over 2022 and
OL,10,F2023, and called for a Treasury-led
OL,11,Freview of the Bank's QT programme, its
OL,12,Fmandate and its independence.
OL,14,FThe Bank of England has been
OL,15,Findependent of government since 1997,
OL,16,Fwith interest rates set by its
OL,17,FMonetary Policy Committee aimed at
OL,18,Fkeeping inflation around 2%.
