OL,3,CTory MPs demand review of Bank of
OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,FA spokesperson for the Bank of England
OL,7,Fsaid the previous programme of
OL,8,Fquantitative easing had seen
OL,9,Fsignificant revenues flow to the
OL,10,FTreasury in the knowledge that this
OL,11,Fwould be reversed in future, and the
OL,12,Foverall profit or loss from the scheme
OL,13,Fwas still uncertain.
OL,15,FThey added that the profit and loss
OL,16,Ffigures did not provide an assessment
OL,17,Fof the impact of the bond-buying
OL,18,Fquantitative easing programme on
OL,19,Freducing borrowing costs and
OL,20,Fsupporting the economy over the past
OL,21,F15 years.
