OL,3,CTory MPs demand review of Bank of
OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,FSeveral of the MPs who signed the
OL,7,Fletter to the chancellor, including
OL,8,FSir Jacob, have previously criticised
OL,9,Fthe Bank of England, blaming it for
OL,10,Fthe high inflation experienced by the
OL,11,FUK in recent years and in some cases
OL,12,Faccusing Bank leaders of working
OL,13,Fagainst the economic policies of
OL,14,Fformer prime minister Liz Truss.
OL,16,FOne of the MPs, Marcus Fysh, described
OL,17,Fthe Bank's quantitative easing policy
OL,18,Fas a "nightmare" and said it had been
OL,19,F"far wider of the mark on controlling
OL,20,Finflation than other central banks
OL,21,Faround the world".
