OL,6,FHe added: "If we're going to hand the
OL,7,Fkeys to our monetary policy to the
OL,8,FBank of England, it's vital there's
OL,9,Frigorous accountability and that it
OL,10,Fdemonstrates monetary expertise."
OL,12,FEd Barker, chief executive of
OL,13,FConservative Way Forward, said
OL,14,Finstitutions must be "held to account
OL,15,Ffor their performance" on inflation.
