OL,3,CTory MPs demand review of Bank of
OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,FHe added: "Forcing British taxpayers
OL,7,Fto bail out the Bank is unique amongst
OL,8,Fthe world's advanced economies. The
OL,9,Fworld's other major central banks are
OL,10,Fshielding their populations from any
OL,11,Flosses involved in QT.
OL,13,F"Why one of the world's oldest central
OL,14,Fbanks is ignoring the Fed (US Federal
OL,15,FReserve Bank) and the ECB (European
OL,16,FCentral Bank) and adopting the
OL,17,Fpractice of the central banks of
OL,18,FAlbania and Azerbaijan is beyond me."
