OL,6,FA Bank of England spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Up until September 2022, the Bank
OL,8,Fsent #123.9 billion to HM Treasury,
OL,9,Fand it was always recognised that
OL,10,Fpayments would reverse in future. The
OL,11,FBank also pays billions of pounds in
OL,12,Fseigniorage income from the issuance
OL,13,Fof banknotes to the Treasury which
OL,14,Fother central banks retain to balance
OL,15,Ftheir books.
OL,17,F"Future payments are highly uncertain
OL,18,Fand stopping active sales won't
OL,19,Fnecessarily change the lifetime profit
OL,20,For loss of the APF."
OL,26,@oD@AOUyD@AOU|D@TO]
