OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,FA Treasury spokesperson said: "The
OL,7,Fseparation of fiscal and monetary
OL,8,Fpolicy is a key feature of the UK's
OL,9,Feconomic framework, and essential for
OL,10,Fthe effective delivery of monetary
OL,11,Fpolicy. Interfering with decisions on
OL,12,FQT, including on the pace and scale of
OL,13,Funwind, would undermine that
OL,14,Fseparation.
OL,26,@nD@_OU
