OL,3,CTory MPs demand review of Bank of
OL,4,CEngland's independence
OL,6,F"That is why it is vital the
OL,7,FGovernment underwrites the Bank of
OL,8,FEngland's asset purchases so it can
OL,9,Fmeet its monetary policy objectives,
OL,10,Fincluding returning inflation to 2% `
OL,11,Fand it is good news that it is back to
OL,12,F3.2% with the UK economy turning a
OL,13,Fcorner.
OL,15,F"More than #120 billion has been
OL,16,Ftransferred to the Treasury from the
OL,17,FBank of England between 2012 and 2022.
OL,18,FHowever, it was always expected that
OL,19,Flosses would be incurred when this was
OL,20,Funwound, and any future gains or
OL,21,Flosses are highly uncertain."
